name: Dell Inspiron 15.6" FHD Touchscreen Business Laptop, Core i5-1035G1 (Beats i7-7500U) Up to 3.6GHz, Windows 10 Pro, 16GB RAM, 512GB SSD, AC WiFi, Bluetooth, Media Card Reader
feature_bullets: [POWERFUL PERFORMANCE]: The Dell Inspiron Laptop is powered with the latest 10th Generation Intel Core i5-1035G1 processor (up to 3.60 GHz Max Boost, 6 MB Cache) and 16GB high-bandwidth DDR4 memory, powerful processing for advanced multitasking, demanding computing, smooth gaming, multiple tabs browsing, and everyday tasks. 512GB PCIe NVMe M.2 SSD (15x faster than HDD, stay cool and quiet) offers ample storage, quick boot-up times, fast data access, and improves the overall performance,[PREMIUM DESIGN]: The slim and portable Dell laptop is only 0.8 inch thin and 3.94 lb light, and you can work seamlessly, anywhere. The PC is extremely durable and designed to last.Full keyboard with 10-key numeric keypad, Type comfortably, input numbers quickly and maneuver through games with ease. Touchpad with multitouch control. Every detail is crafted for comfort and style, with all the power you need to get things done,[STUNNING VISUALS]: 15.6" Full HD touch screen for hands-on control. Natural finger-touch navigation makes the most of Windows 10. The 1920 x 1080 resolution boasts impressive color and clarity with Wide Viewing angles display. Energy-efficient LED backlight. With ExpressCharging Mode, get your battery from 0% up to 80% within an hour so that you're not tied down to an outlet while out and about.,[COLLABORATION READY]: Windows 10 Pro 64-bit (best version of Windows OS, optimal for Business and Education) protects your data with enterprise-grade security, boosts productivity with powerful management tools, and keeps going with long battery life. Integrated Widescreen HD 720P Webcam with Dual Digital Microphone Array, A new 4-element lens delivers sharp video in all areas of the frame, especially in dim lighting conditions.,[HIGH EFFICIENCY]: The windows laptop PC is sensibly optimized for productivity and flexibility with 1x USB 2.0 Type A and 2x USB 3.2 Type A for fast data transfer, 1x multi-format SD Media Card Reader for easy transfer of photos/videos, 1x HDMI, universal Audio Jack delivers true sound quality, 1x RJ-45 Gigabit Ethernet. 1-year manufacturer warranty.

name: Lenovo IdeaPad 15.6" Laptop Newest, 20GB RAM, 1TB SSD, AMD Dual-core Processor, 15.6 Inch HD Anti-Glare Display, WiFi6 Bluetooth 5.0, 9.5Hr Battery, Windows 11 +GM Accessories
feature_bullets: 【Upgraded to 20GB memory for advanced multitasking】 Substantial high-bandwidth RAM to smoothly run your games and photo- and video-editing applications, as well as multiple programs and browser tabs all at once.,UPGRDED VERSION【Upgraded to 1TB PCIe SSD (on system) + 128GB Emmc Storage】 Save files fast and store more data. With massive amounts of storage and advanced communication power, PCI-e SSDs are great for major gaming applications, multiple servers, daily backups, and more,【Open Wi-Fi settings】You may use the Command Prompt to open Wi-Fi settings on Windows 11 by following these steps: 2.Click and FN+Shift+F10 or Shift+F10 at the same time. | 2.In the Command Prompt window, type “start ms-settings:network-wifi” and press Enter. | 3.The Wi-Fi settings page will open in the Settings app.,【AMD Dual-core Processor】 AMD Athlon Silver 3050U (2.3 GHz, up to 3.2 GHz). This laptop is powered by AMD which gives good performance with efficiency. It can also do simple gaming thanks to its integrated AMD Radeon graphics.Integrated graphics chipset with shared video memory provides solid image quality for Internet use, movies, basic photo editing and casual gaming.,【15.6 IN HD Screen】View all your photos, movies, and games in crisp HD (1366 x 768) resolution on a narrow-edge. Energy-efficient LED backlight.
